<bibRefCitation id="EF986DA8FFC4FFA16580FB25C0C7FA8B" author="Chatterjee, T." box="[1223,1436,1267,1294]" pageId="8" pageNumber="309" pagination="107 - 108" refId="ref10142" refString="Chatterjee, T. (1996 b) Ciliate infestation on phytal Halacaridae (Acari) from the Kovalam beach (Kerala coast). Journal of the Bombay Natural History Society, 93, 107 - 108." type="journal article" year="1996">Chatterjee (1996b)</bibRefCitation>
